{"title":"早晨","authors":["骆晓戈"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":9,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"早晨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖南师范学院  骆晓戈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨，来了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖畔饮水的白鹅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚睁开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清亮清亮的眼睛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨，来了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浮出清波的荷花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包含着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光芒四射的黎明……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨读的姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你难道不爱这风景？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨读的姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你难道忘了这早晨？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只愿轻声的诵读，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化作百鸟的啼唱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只愿理想的早霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与红日一起升腾；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只愿青春的身影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教江山多娇，使花儿更俊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，晨读的姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就是祖国的早晨。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}